00:00:28.250 --> 00:00:31.280 align:middle line:10%
>> There is a very curious
phenomenon in the world which

00:00:31.280 --> 00:00:33.440 align:middle line:10%
is coming more and
more to the fore,

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:36.150 align:middle line:10%
that things happen
at the same time.

00:00:36.150 --> 00:00:38.960 align:middle line:10%
They fall together, as it
were, even though there

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:41.660 align:middle line:10%
is no way that we would
know how they would actually

00:00:41.660 --> 00:00:43.010 align:middle line:10%
be connected.

00:00:43.010 --> 00:00:46.110 align:middle line:84%
Great discoveries happened
at the same time period,

00:00:46.110 --> 00:00:50.580 align:middle line:84%
with architecture, with the
pyramids being born in--

00:00:50.580 --> 00:00:56.240 align:middle line:84%
in middle America, in some
parts of Europe, and in the east

00:00:56.240 --> 00:01:00.680 align:middle line:84%
and following the same laws,
practically, all at once

00:01:00.680 --> 00:01:02.850 align:middle line:90%
in historical time.

00:01:02.850 --> 00:01:05.390 align:middle line:84%
Same discoveries--
the great appearance

00:01:05.390 --> 00:01:09.040 align:middle line:84%
of the great teachers
in Greece and in China

00:01:09.040 --> 00:01:10.680 align:middle line:90%
almost at the same time.

00:01:10.680 --> 00:01:13.620 align:middle line:84%
Now, as far as we know, they
didn't talk to each other.

00:01:13.620 --> 00:01:16.110 align:middle line:90%
They didn't have the internet.

00:01:16.110 --> 00:01:19.280 align:middle line:84%
So how come did these
things happen together?

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:23.700 align:middle line:84%
Coincidences that are
meaningful are synchronicity.

00:01:23.700 --> 00:01:26.510 align:middle line:84%
So the question is,
what is synchronicity?

00:01:26.510 --> 00:01:29.200 align:middle line:90%
It's acausal connection.

00:01:29.200 --> 00:01:31.910 align:middle line:84%
That is almost the
official definition of it,

00:01:31.910 --> 00:01:34.010 align:middle line:90%
no cause and effect, no--

00:01:34.010 --> 00:01:36.170 align:middle line:90%
knowable cause and effect.

00:01:36.170 --> 00:01:38.300 align:middle line:84%
Of course, there's
a deeper cause.

00:01:38.300 --> 00:01:41.170 align:middle line:84%
My consciousness is
collected with yours,

00:01:41.170 --> 00:01:44.120 align:middle line:84%
as we are part of the
same cosmic hologram.

00:01:44.120 --> 00:01:47.630 align:middle line:84%
But this is not the
normal push and pull

00:01:47.630 --> 00:01:54.980 align:middle line:84%
connection, not by energy and
words creating a difference.

00:01:54.980 --> 00:01:57.320 align:middle line:84%
It's a spontaneous
connection between two

00:01:57.320 --> 00:02:01.130 align:middle line:84%
seemingly unconnected things
that connect together.

00:02:01.130 --> 00:02:04.950 align:middle line:84%
And together, they
lead to something.

00:02:04.950 --> 00:02:06.360 align:middle line:90%
This is a true synchronicity.

00:02:06.360 --> 00:02:08.487 align:middle line:84%
Entire big volumes,
learned volumes,

00:02:08.487 --> 00:02:10.070 align:middle line:84%
have been written
on this because it's

00:02:10.070 --> 00:02:11.810 align:middle line:90%
a remarkable phenomenon.

00:02:11.810 --> 00:02:15.238 align:middle line:84%
And we can't dismiss
it as just imagination.

00:02:15.238 --> 00:02:17.560 align:middle line:90%
[CHIMING]

00:02:17.560 --> 00:02:20.290 align:middle line:84%
The world is an illusion
is one possible answer

00:02:20.290 --> 00:02:23.210 align:middle line:84%
to the question,
what is the world?

00:02:23.210 --> 00:02:25.460 align:middle line:84%
Maybe everything that
we perceive of the world

00:02:25.460 --> 00:02:28.910 align:middle line:84%
is an illusion
created by our mind.

00:02:28.910 --> 00:02:33.410 align:middle line:84%
Or maybe the
illusion is our mind,

00:02:33.410 --> 00:02:39.410 align:middle line:84%
and the world is really there as
a bit of unsensing, non-living,

00:02:39.410 --> 00:02:42.260 align:middle line:90%
just brute matter, as it were.

00:02:42.260 --> 00:02:44.290 align:middle line:84%
The Buddha took the
answer, thinking--

00:02:44.290 --> 00:02:47.390 align:middle line:84%
saying that the
world as we perceive

00:02:47.390 --> 00:02:50.270 align:middle line:84%
