00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:01.230 align:middle line:90%
But that's an illusion.

00:03:01.230 --> 00:03:04.280 align:middle line:84%
The reality lies
deeper, more profoundly.

00:03:04.280 --> 00:03:06.200 align:middle line:84%
And that-- by the
way, that thought

00:03:06.200 --> 00:03:09.090 align:middle line:84%
is now shared at the
leading edge of science,

00:03:09.090 --> 00:03:11.790 align:middle line:84%
especially in quantum
science, when we talk

00:03:11.790 --> 00:03:13.430 align:middle line:90%
about the fundamental field.

00:03:13.430 --> 00:03:15.035 align:middle line:90%
But it's also there in--

00:03:15.035 --> 00:03:19.050 align:middle line:84%
in the grand unified
theories, in the theories

00:03:19.050 --> 00:03:20.390 align:middle line:90%
of solid-state matter.

00:03:20.390 --> 00:03:25.090 align:middle line:84%
