had to originate someplace.

00:03:25.090 --> 00:03:27.710 align:middle line:84%
And it originates
at a deeper level.

00:03:27.710 --> 00:03:30.650 align:middle line:84%
And then the deeper
level is the real world,

00:03:30.650 --> 00:03:32.640 align:middle line:90%
and matter is an illusion.

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:37.769 align:middle line:84%
This statement would now be
accepted by leading physicists.

00:03:37.769 --> 00:03:40.040 align:middle line:90%
[CHIMING]

