master, for days on end.

00:04:25.986 --> 00:04:28.470 align:middle line:90%
[CHIMING]

00:04:28.470 --> 00:04:31.160 align:middle line:84%
This-- makes this
misinterpretation

00:04:31.160 --> 00:04:32.660 align:middle line:90%
of the world as an illusion.

