something, then, of course,

00:05:03.070 --> 00:05:04.280 align:middle line:90%
we'll pay the consequence.

00:05:04.280 --> 00:05:06.280 align:middle line:90%
We'll pay the price.

00:05:06.280 --> 00:05:09.580 align:middle line:90%
So it's-- the world is--

00:05:09.580 --> 00:05:12.640 align:middle line:90%
as it is out there is out there.

00:05:12.640 --> 00:05:15.108 align:middle line:84%
How we think of it
can be an illusion.

00:05:15.108 --> 00:05:18.390 align:middle line:90%
[CHIMING]

00:05:18.390 --> 00:05:24.460 align:middle line:84%
We have divorced ourselves
from our true nature.

00:05:24.460 --> 00:05:26.380 align:middle line:90%
We are not here by accident.

00:05:26.380 --> 00:05:29.410 align:middle line:84%
We are here for the same reason
that the galaxies are here

00:05:29.410 --> 00:05:32.555 align:middle line:84%
and that the single-celled
organisms are here

00:05:32.555 --> 00:05:34.610 align:middle line:90%
and the plants are here.

00:05:34.610 --> 00:05:37.460 align:middle line:84%
We are here as part of
an evolutionary process.

00:05:37.460 --> 00:05:39.270 align:middle line:90%
But we have ignored--

00:05:39.270 --> 00:05:40.570 align:middle line:90%
we are ignoring this.

00:05:40.570 --> 00:05:42.320 align:middle line:84%
We are also rejecting
the idea that

00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:46.970 align:middle line:84%
there being a higher purpose
built into the universe.

00:05:46.970 --> 00:05:49.160 align:middle line:84%
And we are destroying
the environment

00:05:49.160 --> 00:05:52.310 align:middle line:84%
because we are no
longer connected

00:05:52.310 --> 00:05:55.670 align:middle line:90%
on that felt experience level.

00:05:55.670 --> 00:06:01.130 align:middle line:84%
Our connection is there, but we
don't feel it, don't sense it.

00:06:01.130 --> 00:06:04.370 align:middle line:84%
We will need to
recover that to become

00:06:04.370 --> 00:06:09.450 align:middle line:84%
more aware of the true nature
of nature, so to speak.

00:06:09.450 --> 00:06:14.160 align:middle line:84%
But the nature of nature is also
the nature of our being here.

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:18.190 align:middle line:84%
We are destroying something
that we don't feel connected to.

00:06:18.190 --> 00:06:23.210 align:middle line:84%
We think it's just there
as-- as a mechanical,

00:06:23.210 --> 00:06:26.870 align:middle line:84%
uncaused consequence and
meaningless consequence

00:06:26.870 --> 00:06:30.410 align:middle line:84%
of the universe operating
in a certain way,

00:06:30.410 --> 00:06:31.860 align:middle line:90%
just happening to be--

00:06:31.860 --> 00:06:35.350 align:middle line:84%
to produce these kind of things,
no further meaning to it.

00:06:35.350 --> 00:06:40.640 align:middle line:84%
We need to recover our oneness,
our contact, our communication,

00:06:40.640 --> 00:06:43.510 align:middle line:84%
if you like, with
the environment.

00:06:43.510 --> 00:06:45.860 align:middle line:90%
[CHIMING]

00:06:45.860 --> 00:06:48.770 align:middle line:84%
I would like to
promote, to help,

00:06:48.770 --> 00:06:52.880 align:middle line:84%
to assist in people
taking themselves

00:06:52.880 --> 00:06:57.860 align:middle line:84%
seriously and exploring
themselves, stopping

00:06:57.860 --> 00:06:58.890 align:middle line:90%
for a moment.

00:06:58.890 --> 00:07:00.800 align:middle line:84%
Stop the world, and
think of who you

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:03.630 align:middle line:84%
are because when
you come back, you

00:07:03.630 --> 00:07:07.200 align:middle line:84%
might act more together
in synchronicity,

00:07:07.200 --> 00:07:10.620 align:middle line:90%
in syntony with the world.

00:07:10.620 --> 00:07:16.130 align:middle line:84%
You have to take a break
from this my-- wild rush

00:07:16.130 --> 00:07:22.170 align:middle line:84%
toward technically and
mechanically exploiting things

00:07:22.170 --> 00:07:26.010 align:middle line:84%
that satisfy our
immediate wants and needs

00:07:26.010 --> 00:07:29.470 align:middle line:84%
and understand
better who we are,

00:07:29.470 --> 00:07:34.480 align:middle line:84%
how we relate to nature, what
nature is, not philosophically,

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:40.980 align:middle line:84%
not having to go even into deep
theoretical considerations.

00:07:40.980 --> 00:07:42.420 align:middle line:90%
Just sense it.

00:07:42.420 --> 00:07:45.690 align:middle line:84%
Sense the world as
it is around you.

00:07:45.690 --> 00:07:46.820 align:middle line:90%
Become one with it.

00:07:46.820 --> 00:07:48.990 align:middle line:90%
Walk in the forest.

00:07:48.990 --> 00:07:51.760 align:middle line:84%
Sit down for a moment,
and look at the sun

00:07:51.760 --> 00:07:54.270 align:middle line:84%
or look at the
brightness around.

00:07:54.270 --> 00:07:58.210 align:middle line:10%
It's a remarkable world,
and it's not a casual world.

00:07:58.210 --> 00:08:00.850 align:middle line:84%
It's a world that has
its meaning and sense.

00:08:00.850 --> 00:08:05.396 align:middle line:84%
So I would say reorient
yourself, the individual,

00:08:05.396 --> 00:08:07.270 align:middle line:84%
and then groups of
individuals, because those

00:08:07.270 --> 00:08:08.660 align:middle line:90%
will change the world.

00:08:08.660 --> 00:08:12.390 align:middle line:84%
Reorient toward an
understanding that you

00:08:12.390 --> 00:08:15.390 align:middle line:84%
are part of a larger
development, which

00:08:15.390 --> 00:08:16.590 align:middle line:90%
you call "evolution."

00:08:16.590 --> 00:08:20.810 align:middle line:84%
And evolution on Earth is part
of evolution in the universe.

00:08:20.810 --> 00:08:23.500 align:middle line:84%
That is what I think
we need to recognize.

00:08:23.500 --> 00:08:26.940 align:middle line:84%
And then we'll come back
and be more careful, more--

00:08:26.940 --> 00:08:32.340 align:middle line:84%
more and better advised,
more sound in our decisions

00:08:32.340 --> 00:08:33.179 align:middle line:90%
as to how to live.

00:08:33.179 --> 00:08:36.870 align:middle line:10%
[CHIMING]

00:08:36.870 --> 00:08:40.340 align:middle line:10%
Some years ago, Marshall
McLuhan, the Canadian,

00:08:40.340 --> 00:08:45.130 align:middle line:10%
the thinker of the connections,
of electronic connections,

00:08:45.130 --> 00:08:48.000 align:middle line:10%
he said, "The medium
is the message."

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:49.670 align:middle line:90%
But I don't agree.

00:08:49.670 --> 00:08:52.530 align:middle line:84%
A medium is an instrument
to convey the message.

00:08:52.530 --> 00:08:55.712 align:middle line:84%
The medium itself
is not the message.

00:08:55.712 --> 00:08:58.500 align:middle line:84%
He thought if you start
connecting to each other,

00:08:58.500 --> 00:09:00.910 align:middle line:90%
then you will be connected.

00:09:00.910 --> 00:09:04.050 align:middle line:84%
But you can be connected
in so many different ways.

00:09:04.050 --> 00:09:07.080 align:middle line:84%
You can be connected as
part of a terrorist group.

00:09:07.080 --> 00:09:09.240 align:middle line:84%
You can be part of
an evangelical group.

00:09:09.240 --> 00:09:11.950 align:middle line:84%
You can be part of
a business group.

00:09:11.950 --> 00:09:14.490 align:middle line:84%
You can be many
things, and they all

00:09:14.490 --> 00:09:16.200 align:middle line:90%
will be based on connection.

00:09:16.200 --> 00:09:18.810 align:middle line:84%
But the internet is an
instrument for connection,

00:09:18.810 --> 00:09:22.230 align:middle line:84%
for the good, for the
indifferent, and for the bad.

00:09:22.230 --> 00:09:25.380 align:middle line:84%
Let's try to make it
work in such a way

00:09:25.380 --> 00:09:28.410 align:middle line:84%
that it promotes our
being in the world

00:09:28.410 --> 00:09:30.480 align:middle line:84%
and being together
with each other

00:09:30.480 --> 00:09:34.620 align:middle line:84%
and creating a sphere
of meaningful life

00:09:34.620 --> 00:09:38.136 align:middle line:84%
on this planet, which we're
in danger of losing that.

00:09:38.136 --> 00:09:41.280 align:middle line:84%
Losing life is becoming
meaningless and becoming

00:09:41.280 --> 00:09:46.440 align:middle line:84%
conflictual and is in danger
of disappearing altogether

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:52.800 align:middle line:84%
as we use more and more powerful
means of enforcing our contact,

00:09:52.800 --> 00:09:55.400 align:middle line:90%
our domination over others.

00:09:55.400 --> 00:09:57.990 align:middle line:84%
The internet could facilitate
all the good things

00:09:57.990 --> 00:10:01.650 align:middle line:84%
in the world, as well as the
best things in the world.

00:10:01.650 --> 00:10:03.630 align:middle line:84%
So the adults in
the room, if they

00:10:03.630 --> 00:10:08.850 align:middle line:84%
use the internet to share their
insights, their conclusions,

00:10:08.850 --> 00:10:11.710 align:middle line:84%
or even just their
explorations, it

00:10:11.710 --> 00:10:14.520 align:middle line:84%
will be a very
great step forward.

00:10:14.520 --> 00:10:16.440 align:middle line:84%
The problem is to
use the internet

00:10:16.440 --> 00:10:19.020 align:middle line:90%
for itself, just as a--

00:10:19.020 --> 00:10:20.070 align:middle line:90%
as a use technology.

00:10:20.070 --> 00:10:22.860 align:middle line:84%
Then it's a kind of a
toy, like you're using--

00:10:22.860 --> 00:10:26.730 align:middle line:84%
a new car comes along that it's
more powerful than the others,

00:10:26.730 --> 00:10:27.750 align:middle line:90%
you know?

00:10:27.750 --> 00:10:28.080 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:10:28.080 --> 00:10:29.370 align:middle line:90%
That's a great fascination.

00:10:29.370 --> 00:10:32.270 align:middle line:84%
I used to love
driving sports cars.

00:10:32.270 --> 00:10:35.760 align:middle line:84%
But I realized that the point
is where this car takes you.

00:10:35.760 --> 00:10:38.850 align:middle line:84%
Now I'm more interested in
where I'm going with the car

00:10:38.850 --> 00:10:41.630 align:middle line:84%
than just the technology
of getting there, you know?

00:10:41.630 --> 00:10:43.380 align:middle line:84%
So the internet--
in the internet

00:10:43.380 --> 00:10:46.050 align:middle line:84%
is a technology for
getting someplace.

00:10:46.050 --> 00:10:49.960 align:middle line:84%
But we have forgotten to
ask, where do we want to go?

00:10:49.960 --> 00:10:52.200 align:middle line:84%
So a great instrument,
almost, I would

00:10:52.200 --> 00:10:56.070 align:middle line:84%
say, an essential instrument,
irreplaceable instrument today

00:10:56.070 --> 00:10:59.670 align:middle line:84%
in a complex world of
seven billion people

00:10:59.670 --> 00:11:02.760 align:middle line:84%
to use this connection,
which is the internet.

00:11:02.760 --> 00:11:06.390 align:middle line:84%
But use it consciously and
not just as a fascination

00:11:06.390 --> 00:11:08.806 align:middle line:90%
for technology itself.

00:11:08.806 --> 00:11:11.290 align:middle line:90%
[CHIMING]

00:11:11.290 --> 00:11:14.930 align:middle line:84%
Well, Plato's analogy
of the cave, of a--

00:11:14.930 --> 00:11:18.170 align:middle line:84%
of a group of
prisoners, we call it,

00:11:18.170 --> 00:11:20.760 align:middle line:84%
who are changed in
such a way in a cave

00:11:20.760 --> 00:11:22.530 align:middle line:90%
